videos.headline: Buckeyes score first with 2-yard TD
videos.description: Curtis Samuel runs for 2 yards to put Ohio State on the board over Maryland.

videos.headline: Barrett keeps it himself for second Buckeyes TD
videos.description: J.T. Barrett runs the ball in for a 4-yard touchdown to extend Ohio State's lead to 14-0 over Maryland.

videos.headline: Dontre Wilson taken to locker room after fumble
videos.description: Dontre Wilson had to be taken to the locker room after several Maryland defenders fell on top of him shortly after a fumble recovered by Ohio State

videos.headline: McCall pushes his way into the end zone
videos.description: Ohio State's Demario McCall extends the Buckeyes' lead to 55-3 over Maryland with a 3-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Victor's first career TD is a 25-yard strike against Maryland
videos.description: Binjimen Victor hauls in a 25-yard TD pass from Joe Burrow to extend Ohio State's lead to 61-3.

videos.headline: Samuel, Barrett fuel OSU rout
videos.description: J.T. Barrett throws two touchdowns to Curtis Samuel and each add two on the ground as Ohio State crushes Maryland 62-3.
